statements: SELECT * FROM VoterVerification WHERE voter_id = 12345;
SELECT first_name, last_name FROM VoterVerification WHERE eligibility_status = TRUE;
SELECT * FROM VoterVerification WHERE last_name LIKE 'S%' ORDER BY first_name ASC;
SELECT voter_id, address FROM VoterVerification WHERE date_of_birth > '1990-01-01';
SELECT first_name, last_name, address FROM VoterVerification WHERE eligibility_status = FALSE ORDER BY last_name DESC, first_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM VoterVerification WHERE voter_id = 12345;
SELECT first_name, last_name, address FROM VoterVerification WHERE date_of_birth > '2000-01-01';
SELECT voter_id, first_name, last_name FROM VoterVerification WHERE eligibility_status = TRUE GROUP BY voter_id;
SELECT * FROM VoterVerification WHERE address LIKE '%Street%';
SELECT * FROM VoterVerification ORDER BY last_name DESC, first_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM voter;
SELECT first_name, last_name, age FROM voter WHERE age > 30;
SELECT last_name, address FROM voter ORDER BY last_name ASC;
SELECT first_name, age, eligible_to_vote FROM voter WHERE eligible_to_vote = TRUE;
SELECT registration_id, registration_date, verification_status FROM voter_registration WHERE verification_status = FALSE;
SELECT first_name, last_name, age, address FROM voter WHERE age > 18;
SELECT * FROM voter WHERE eligible_to_vote = true ORDER BY last_name ASC;
SELECT voter_id, verification_status FROM voter_registration WHERE verification_status = false;
SELECT registration_id, registration_date FROM voter_registration WHERE registration_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31';
SELECT first_name, last_name, address FROM voter ORDER BY last_name DESC, first_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM Voter;
SELECT first_name, last_name FROM Voter ORDER BY last_name ASC;
SELECT vote_candidate FROM VoteHistory WHERE vote_cast_time >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT voter_id, age, address FROM Voter WHERE age >= 18;
SELECT voter_id, is_eligible, eligibility_reason FROM VoterEligibility WHERE is_eligible = TRUE;
SELECT first_name, last_name FROM Voter ORDER BY last_name ASC, first_name DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT voter_id, first_name, last_name, age, address FROM Voter WHERE age > 18 AND age < 30 ORDER BY age DESC, last_name ASC;

SELECT vh.vote_id, v.first_name, v.last_name, vh.vote_cast_time, vh.vote_candidate FROM VoteHistory vh INNER JOIN Voter v ON vh.voter_id = v.voter_id WHERE vh.vote_cast_time > '2022-01-01 00:00:00' ORDER BY vh.vote_cast_time DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT ve.voter_id, v.first_name, v.last_name, ve.is_eligible, ve.eligibility_reason FROM VoterEligibility ve INNER JOIN Voter v ON ve.voter_id = v.voter_id WHERE ve.is_eligible = TRUE;

SELECT v.first_name, v.last_name, vh.vote_candidate, COUNT(vh.vote_candidate) AS vote_count FROM Voter v JOIN VoteHistory vh ON v.voter_id = vh.voter_id GROUP BY vh.vote_candidate ORDER BY vote_count DESC;
SELECT * FROM voters ORDER BY date_of_birth DESC;
SELECT voter_name, address FROM voters WHERE is_eligible = TRUE;
SELECT voter_id, date_of_birth FROM voters WHERE address LIKE '%Street';
SELECT * FROM vote_records WHERE verifying_officer = 'John Doe';
SELECT * FROM voter_ids WHERE id_type = 'Passport' LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM voters ORDER BY voter_name ASC LIMIT 10;
SELECT voter_name, date_of_birth FROM voters WHERE is_eligible = TRUE AND date_of_birth <= '2000-01-01';
SELECT v.voter_id, v.voter_name, vr.voted_at FROM voters v JOIN vote_records vr ON v.voter_id = vr.voter_id WHERE vr.voted_at >= '2022-01-01' ORDER BY vr.voted_at DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT v.voter_name, vi.id_type, vi.id_number FROM voters v JOIN voter_ids vi ON v.voter_id = vi.voter_id WHERE vi.id_type = 'Passport' AND vi.expiry_date > '2022-12-31';
SELECT v.voter_name, ec.criteria_name FROM voters v JOIN eligibility_criteria ec ON v.date_of_birth <= (NOW() - INTERVAL ec.minimum_age YEAR);
SELECT * FROM voter_information;
SELECT first_name, last_name, address FROM voter_information WHERE is_registered = TRUE;
SELECT * FROM voter_eligibility WHERE is_eligible = TRUE;
SELECT voter_id, last_voted_date FROM voter_history ORDER BY last_voted_date DESC;
SELECT voter_id, id_type FROM voter_issued_id WHERE id_type = 'Driver's License';
SELECT * FROM voter_information ORDER BY last_name DESC, first_name ASC LIMIT 10;
SELECT first_name, last_name, address FROM voter_information WHERE date_of_birth > '1990-01-01';
SELECT vi.first_name, vi.last_name, ve.is_eligible FROM voter_information vi JOIN voter_eligibility ve ON vi.id = ve.voter_id WHERE ve.is_eligible = TRUE;
SELECT vi.first_name, vi.last_name, vh.last_voted_date FROM voter_information vi LEFT JOIN voter_history vh ON vi.id = vh.voter_id WHERE vh.voting_frequency > 5;
SELECT vi.first_name, vi.last_name, vi.address, vv.verification_status FROM voter_information vi INNER JOIN voter_verification vv ON vi.id = vv.voter_id WHERE vv.verification_date < '2022-01-01';
